title: Looking for players for Norms or flex
body: Hey guys I'm looking for some fun but competitive people to play with I live in Canberra and was hoping for fellow camberrians  to play with but anyone is welcomed! I currently work a full time job but hope we can still end up playing!

replies.body:
Omg, i am from Canberra too also working full time.

Recently I only really play on the weekends due to so much work committements.

But, we must play together, I have added you....
